===message:I agree with your view of Evans and his speech.  While he did not ever acknowledge that his goal was to try to “hold onto his ethnic pride, culture, & religion”, his means of trying to do this were so backward and wrong.  He may have wanted to live a “free and prosperous life here in America” but he did not want anyone else of the “wrong race” to have that same right.  It is because he was this selfish and intolerant of others that his cause and his organization, the KKK, failed miserably.
